description: The EU aims for a deal this year to force the immediate removal of "terrorism propaganda" online.
title: New EU drive to remove extremist web content
title_page: New EU drive to remove extremist web content - BBC News
maintext: French investigators have established that Brahim Aouissaoui, the Tunisian who fatally stabbed three people in a church in Nice last month, had only arrived in Europe in September. He was shot and wounded by police and is in hospital in the southern French city.
